┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                                RunHaven Guide                                │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
┌ Actions ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│Launch has four steps: choose agent, choose workspace, review safety,         │
│confirm launch.                                                               │
│                                                                              │
│Home shows the RunHaven logo, selected agent, workspace, network, boundary,   │
│and next safe action.                                                         │
│                                                                              │
│Footers show only actions for the current screen. Use ? or F1 to return       │
│here.                                                                         │
│                                                                              │
│Safe plans start with enter. Riskier choices ask you to type run.             │
│                                                                              │
│Other screens: d dashboard/logs, h history/diffs, and g checks/doctor.        │
│                                                                              │
│Display: p shows or hides Cubby. USAGE explains color, motion, line mode,     │
│and light or dark mode.                                                       │
│                                                                              │
│                                                                              │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
    w workspace · r review · d dash · h history · g checks · p pet · esc home
                 Every screen action has a matching CLI command.
